    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Xpressbees International Enterprises. We are on the lookout for a dedicated E-commerce Executive to strengthen our Navi Mumbai-based team.\n\nAbout Xpressbees International Enterprises:\nXpressbees International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Magento\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Xpressbees International Enterprises!",
